<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=5" />
    <title>Adybros Marketing — Turning Businesses into Leads & Sales Machines</title>
    <meta name="description"
        content="Adybros is a performance-driven digital marketing agency. 400+ ads delivered, lakhs spent on campaigns, crores generated in sales." />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo+Black&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* ===========================================================
   ADYBROS — single-file build
   Palette: pure black · pure white · signature red (only)
   =========================================================== */

        :root {
            --black: #000000;
            --ink: #0a0a0a;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --off: #f3f3f3;
            --red: #e30613;
            --red-deep: #b00510;
            --muted: #9a9a9a;
            --muted-dark: #4a4a4a;
            --line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            --line-dark: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);

            --f-display: 'Archivo Black', 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            --f-body: 'Space Grotesk', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            --f-serif: 'Instrument Serif', 'Times New Roman', serif;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%
        }

        body {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            font-family: var(--f-body);
            font-weight: 400;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        ::selection {
            background: var(--red);
            color: var(--white)
        }

        a {
            color: inherit;
            text-decoration: none
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            display: block
        }

        button {
            font: inherit;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            background: none;
            color: inherit
        }

        /* ---- Grain overlay ---- */
        .grain {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 9998;
            opacity: .06;
            mix-blend-mode: overlay;
            background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='3'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
        }

        /* ---- Custom cursor (desktop only) ---- */
        .cursor,
        .cursor-dot {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 9999;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%)
        }

        .cursor {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--red);
            border-radius: 50%;
            transition: width .25s, height .25s, background .25s, border-color .25s;
            mix-blend-mode: difference
        }

        .cursor-dot {
            width: 5px;
            height: 5px;
            background: var(--red);
            border-radius: 50%
        }

        .cursor.hover {
            width: 54px;
            height: 54px;
            background: var(--red);
            border-color: var(--red);
            mix-blend-mode: normal
        }

        @media(hover:none), (max-width:900px) {

            .cursor,
            .cursor-dot {
                display: none
            }

            body {
                cursor: auto
            }
        }

        /* ---- Announcement bar ---- */
        .announce {
            background: var(--red);
            color: var(--white);
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .announce a {
            text-decoration: underline
        }

        .announce::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, .15), transparent);
            transform: translateX(-100%);
            animation: shimmer 3s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes shimmer {
            to {
                transform: translateX(100%)
            }
        }

        /* ---- Navigation ---- */
        .nav {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 18px 36px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, .88);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
            transition: transform .35s cubic-bezier(.2, .8, .2, 1);
        }

        .nav__logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: 17px;
            letter-spacing: .5px
        }

        .nav__logo em {
            font-style: normal;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: var(--red);
            vertical-align: super;
            margin-left: 2px
        }

        .nav__links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 34px;
            font-size: 13px;
            letter-spacing: .3px;
            font-weight: 500
        }

        .nav__links a {
            position: relative;
            padding: 6px 0;
            transition: color .2s
        }

        .nav__links a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 1.5px;
            background: var(--red);
            transition: width .3s cubic-bezier(.7, 0, .2, 1)
        }

        .nav__links a:hover::after {
            width: 100%
        }

        .nav__cta {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 12px 22px;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--white);
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-radius: 100px;
            transition: all .25s
        }

        .nav__cta:hover {
            background: var(--red);
            border-color: var(--red);
            transform: translateY(-2px)
        }

        .nav__burger {
            display: none;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 5px;
            padding: 10px;
            cursor: pointer
        }

        .nav__burger i {
            width: 24px;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--white);
            transition: .3s
        }

        .nav__burger.active i:nth-child(1) {
            transform: translateY(7px) rotate(45deg)
        }

        .nav__burger.active i:nth-child(2) {
            opacity: 0
        }

        .nav__burger.active i:nth-child(3) {
            transform: translateY(-7px) rotate(-45deg)
        }

        /* ---- Mobile drawer ---- */
        .mobile-menu {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: min(360px, 86vw);
            background: var(--black);
            border-left: 1px solid var(--line);
            z-index: 1500;
            padding: 100px 36px 40px;
            transform: translateX(100%);
            transition: transform .45s cubic-bezier(.7, 0, .2, 1);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .mobile-menu.open {
            transform: translateX(0)
        }

        .mobile-menu a {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: 28px;
            letter-spacing: -.02em;
            padding: 14px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line)
        }

        .mobile-menu a:hover {
            color: var(--red)
        }

        .mobile-menu .cta {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 16px;
            background: var(--red);
            text-align: center;
            font-family: var(--f-body);
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700
        }

        /* ---- Hero ---- */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 92vh;
            padding: 100px 36px 60px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 30%;
            right: -200px;
            width: 700px;
            height: 700px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(227, 6, 19, .25), transparent 60%);
            filter: blur(40px);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero__bg {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            opacity: .12;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
            background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=1600&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, black 40%, transparent);
            -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, black 40%, transparent);
        }

        .hero__meta {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 2.5px;
            color: var(--muted);
            max-width: 1400px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1
        }

        .hero__meta-id {
            color: var(--red)
        }

        .hero__title {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(52px, 11vw, 190px);
            line-height: .88;
            letter-spacing: -.04em;
            margin: 30px 0;
            max-width: 1400px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .hero__title .line {
            display: block;
            animation: rise .9s cubic-bezier(.2, .8, .2, 1) backwards
        }

        .line--1 {
            animation-delay: .05s
        }

        .line--2 {
            animation-delay: .15s;
            color: var(--red);
            font-style: italic;
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: -.02em
        }

        .line--3 {
            animation-delay: .25s;
            padding-left: 4vw
        }

        .line--3 em {
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 400;
            text-decoration: underline;
            text-decoration-color: var(--red);
            text-underline-offset: 6px;
            text-decoration-thickness: 4px
        }

        .line--4 {
            animation-delay: .35s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 24px;
            flex-wrap: wrap
        }

        .line--4 .slash {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0 24px;
            background: var(--red);
            color: var(--white);
            transform: skew(-8deg)
        }

        .line--4 .arrow {
            width: clamp(60px, 10vw, 140px);
            height: auto;
            color: var(--white);
            flex-shrink: 0
        }

        .line--4 .machines {
            font-style: italic;
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-weight: 400
        }

        @keyframes rise {
            from {
                transform: translateY(40px);
                opacity: 0
            }

            to {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1
            }
        }

        .hero__foot {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 40px;
            max-width: 1400px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            animation: rise 1s cubic-bezier(.2, .8, .2, 1) .6s backwards;
        }

        .hero__blurb {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 14px;
            max-width: 440px
        }

        .hero__blurb .dot {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 7px;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background: var(--red);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite
        }

        .hero__blurb p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5
        }

        .hero__blurb p em {
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--red);
            font-size: 18px
        }

        @keyframes pulse {

            0%,
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1)
            }

            50% {
                opacity: .5;
                transform: scale(1.5)
            }
        }

        .hero__cta-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 14px;
            flex-wrap: wrap
        }

        .hero__scroll {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: var(--muted);
            animation: bob 2.2s infinite
        }

        @keyframes bob {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0)
            }

            50% {
                transform: translateY(8px)
            }
        }

        .hero__side {
            position: absolute;
            top: 120px;
            right: 36px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 30px;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1
        }

        .stamp {
            color: var(--white);
            animation: spin 20s linear infinite
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            to {
                transform: rotate(360deg)
            }
        }

        /* ---- Buttons ---- */
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 16px 26px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border: 1.5px solid;
            transition: all .25s;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .btn--primary {
            background: var(--red);
            border-color: var(--red);
            color: var(--white)
        }

        .btn--primary:hover {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--black);
            border-color: var(--white);
            transform: translateY(-3px)
        }

        .btn--ghost {
            background: transparent;
            border-color: var(--white);
            color: var(--white)
        }

        .btn--ghost:hover {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--black)
        }

        .btn--dark {
            background: var(--black);
            border-color: var(--black);
            color: var(--white)
        }

        .btn--dark:hover {
            background: var(--red);
            border-color: var(--red)
        }

        /* ---- Marquee strip ---- */
        .marquee {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
            background: var(--black);
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 22px 0
        }

        .marquee__track {
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(18px, 2.4vw, 28px);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            animation: scroll 40s linear infinite
        }

        .marquee__track span {
            flex-shrink: 0
        }

        .marquee__track .bullet {
            color: var(--red);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: .7em
        }

        @keyframes scroll {
            from {
                transform: translateX(0)
            }

            to {
                transform: translateX(-50%)
            }
        }

        /* ---- Section shared ---- */
        section {
            position: relative
        }

        .section-head {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto 80px
        }

        .section-head.center {
            text-align: center
        }

        .eyebrow {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--red);
            margin-bottom: 24px
        }

        .eyebrow::before {
            content: '';
            width: 30px;
            height: 1.5px;
            background: var(--red)
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 86px);
            line-height: .95;
            letter-spacing: -.03em
        }

        .section-title em {
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--red)
        }

        .section-lead {
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--muted);
            max-width: 620px;
            margin-top: 24px
        }

        .chapter {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: var(--red);
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--red);
            border-radius: 100px
        }

        /* ---- Stats ---- */
        .stats {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--black);
            padding: 120px 36px
        }

        .stats .eyebrow {
            color: var(--red)
        }

        .stats__grid {
            max-width: 1300px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            border-top: 1.5px solid var(--line-dark)
        }

        .stat {
            padding: 36px 28px 28px;
            border-right: 1.5px solid var(--line-dark);
            position: relative;
            transition: background .3s
        }

        .stat:last-child {
            border-right: none
        }

        .stat:hover {
            background: rgba(227, 6, 19, .04)
        }

        .stat:hover .stat__bar i {
            width: 100% !important
        }

        .stat__num {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(52px, 7.5vw, 96px);
            line-height: 1;
            letter-spacing: -.04em;
            margin-bottom: 14px
        }

        .stat__num .prefix {
            color: var(--red);
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: .6em;
            vertical-align: super;
            margin-right: 2px
        }

        .stat__label {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--muted-dark);
            margin-bottom: 20px
        }

        .stat__bar {
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--line-dark);
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .stat__bar i {
            display: block;
            height: 100%;
            width: 0;
            background: var(--red);
            transition: width 1.2s cubic-bezier(.2, .8, .2, 1)
        }

        /* ---- About split ---- */
        .about {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 140px 36px
        }

        .about__inner {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 80px;
            align-items: center
        }

        .about__media {
            position: relative
        }

        .about__media-main {
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 4/5;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: grayscale(100%) contrast(1.1);
            transition: filter .5s
        }

        .about__media:hover .about__media-main {
            filter: grayscale(0%) contrast(1)
        }

        .about__media-stamp {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -30px;
            right: -30px;
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            background: var(--red);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: var(--white);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 20s linear infinite;
        }

        .about__media-stamp::before {
            content: 'EST. 2022 · ADYBROS ·'
        }

        .about__tag {
            position: absolute;
            top: 30px;
            left: 30px;
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--black);
            padding: 10px 16px;
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .about__body h2 {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 68px);
            line-height: .95;
            letter-spacing: -.03em;
            margin-bottom: 32px
        }

        .about__body h2 em {
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--red)
        }

        .about__body p {
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--muted)
        }

        .about__body p em {
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--white);
            font-size: 19px
        }

        .about__body .btn {
            margin-top: 16px
        }

        /* ---- CTA banner (reusable) ---- */
        .cta-banner {
            background: var(--red);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 60px 36px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .cta-banner__strip {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 80px);
            letter-spacing: -.03em;
            line-height: 1;
            animation: scroll 30s linear infinite;
        }

        .cta-banner__strip span {
            flex-shrink: 0
        }

        .cta-banner__strip span:nth-child(even) {
            -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--white);
            color: transparent;
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 400
        }

        .cta-banner__row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 32px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1
        }

        .cta-banner__row p {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            max-width: 480px
        }

        /* ---- Services / grid ---- */
        .services {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 140px 36px
        }

        .services__grid {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 2px;
            background: var(--line)
        }

        .service-card {
            background: var(--black);
            padding: 40px 32px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 420px;
            transition: background .4s;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            background: #0c0c0c
        }

        .service-card__img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 180px;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: grayscale(100%) brightness(.7);
            transition: filter .5s, transform .5s;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .service-card:hover .service-card__img {
            filter: grayscale(0%) brightness(1);
            transform: scale(1.03)
        }

        .service-card__no {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--red);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 10px
        }

        .service-card h3 {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: 26px;
            letter-spacing: -.02em;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.1
        }

        .service-card p {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--muted);
            flex: 1
        }

        .service-card__arrow {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--red);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .service-card__arrow svg {
            transition: transform .3s
        }

        .service-card:hover .service-card__arrow svg {
            transform: translateX(6px)
        }

        /* ---- Process (Seven Stations) ---- */
        .process {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--black);
            padding: 140px 36px
        }

        .process .eyebrow {
            color: var(--red)
        }

        .stations {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto
        }

        .station {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr 280px;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 40px;
            padding: 36px 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line-dark);
            position: relative;
            transition: padding .4s cubic-bezier(.2, .8, .2, 1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .station:last-child {
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-dark)
        }

        .station::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: var(--red);
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transform-origin: left;
            transition: transform .5s cubic-bezier(.2, .8, .2, 1);
            z-index: 0
        }

        .station:hover::before {
            transform: scaleX(1)
        }

        .station:hover {
            padding-left: 40px;
            padding-right: 40px
        }

        .station:hover .station__no,
        .station:hover .station__body,
        .station:hover .station__img {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1
        }

        .station:hover .station__no,
        .station:hover h3,
        .station:hover p {
            color: var(--white)
        }

        .station__no {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: 64px;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--red);
            transition: color .4s
        }

        .station__body h3 {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 42px);
            letter-spacing: -.02em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            line-height: 1;
            transition: color .4s
        }

        .station__body p {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.55;
            color: var(--muted-dark);
            max-width: 620px;
            transition: color .4s
        }

        .station__img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 120px;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: grayscale(100%);
            transition: filter .4s, transform .4s
        }

        .station:hover .station__img {
            filter: grayscale(0%) brightness(1.05);
            transform: scale(1.03)
        }

        /* ---- CTA block A ---- */
        .cta-block {
            background: var(--black);
            padding: 100px 36px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line)
        }

        .cta-block h2 {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 68px);
            line-height: .95;
            letter-spacing: -.03em;
            margin-bottom: 24px
        }

        .cta-block h2 em {
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--red)
        }

        .cta-block p {
            font-size: 17px;
            color: var(--muted);
            max-width: 520px;
            margin: 0 auto 32px
        }

        .cta-block__row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 14px;
            flex-wrap: wrap
        }

        /* ---- Packages ---- */
        .packages {
            background: var(--off);
            color: var(--black);
            padding: 140px 36px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative
        }

        .packages::before {
            content: 'PRICING';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50px;
            right: -40px;
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(80px, 18vw, 200px);
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, .04);
            letter-spacing: -.05em;
            pointer-events: none
        }

        .pkg-grid {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            align-items: stretch;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1
        }

        .pkg {
            background: var(--white);
            border: 1.5px solid var(--black);
            padding: 40px 34px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
            transition: transform .4s cubic-bezier(.2, .8, .2, 1), box-shadow .4s
        }

        .pkg:hover {
            transform: translate(-6px, -6px);
            box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--black)
        }

        .pkg--hero {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            border-color: var(--black);
            transform: translateY(-20px)
        }

        .pkg--hero:hover {
            transform: translate(-6px, -26px);
            box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--red)
        }

        .pkg__ribbon {
            position: absolute;
            top: -14px;
            right: 24px;
            background: var(--red);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 6px 14px;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px
        }

        .pkg__tag {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--red);
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 14px
        }

        .pkg__name {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: 40px;
            letter-spacing: -.03em;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 22px
        }

        .pkg__price {
            display: flex;
            align-items: baseline;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 4px
        }

        .price-main {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: 34px;
            letter-spacing: -.03em
        }

        .price-sub {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--muted-dark)
        }

        .pkg--hero .price-sub {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .6)
        }

        .price-sub i {
            font-style: normal;
            font-size: 10px;
            margin-left: 4px;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border: 1px solid currentColor;
            border-radius: 3px;
            opacity: .7
        }

        .pkg__quarter {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--muted-dark);
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            padding-bottom: 22px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed currentColor;
            opacity: .8
        }

        .pkg--hero .pkg__quarter {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .7)
        }

        .pkg__list {
            list-style: none;
            flex: 1;
            margin-bottom: 30px
        }

        .pkg__list li {
            padding: 11px 0 11px 24px;
            font-size: 13.5px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            position: relative;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, .08)
        }

        .pkg--hero .pkg__list li {
            border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .1)
        }

        .pkg__list li::before {
            content: '→';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--red);
            font-weight: 700
        }

        .pkg__list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none
        }

        .pkg__list li em {
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--red);
            font-weight: 500
        }

        .pkg__list li b {
            font-weight: 600
        }

        .pkg__cta {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 16px;
            border: 1.5px solid currentColor;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: all .25s
        }

        .pkg__cta:hover {
            background: var(--red);
            border-color: var(--red);
            color: var(--white)
        }

        .pkg__cta--solid {
            background: var(--red);
            border-color: var(--red);
            color: var(--white)
        }

        .pkg__cta--solid:hover {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--black);
            border-color: var(--white)
        }

        /* ---- Work / Case study gallery ---- */
        .work {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 140px 36px
        }

        .work__grid {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
            gap: 16px
        }

        .case {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            cursor: pointer;
            aspect-ratio: 1
        }

        .case:nth-child(1) {
            grid-column: span 4;
            aspect-ratio: 2/1
        }

        .case:nth-child(2) {
            grid-column: span 2;
            aspect-ratio: 1
        }

        .case:nth-child(3) {
            grid-column: span 2;
            aspect-ratio: 1
        }

        .case:nth-child(4) {
            grid-column: span 2;
            aspect-ratio: 1
        }

        .case:nth-child(5) {
            grid-column: span 2;
            aspect-ratio: 1
        }

        .case:nth-child(6) {
            grid-column: span 3;
            aspect-ratio: 3/2
        }

        .case:nth-child(7) {
            grid-column: span 3;
            aspect-ratio: 3/2
        }

        .case img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: grayscale(100%) contrast(1.05);
            transition: all .6s cubic-bezier(.2, .8, .2, 1)
        }

        .case:hover img {
            filter: grayscale(0%) contrast(1);
            transform: scale(1.05)
        }

        .case__overlay {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0, 0, 0, .9) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 60%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            padding: 24px;
            transition: background .4s;
        }

        .case:hover .case__overlay {
            background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(227, 6, 19, .9) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, .2) 80%)
        }

        .case__tag {
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--red);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: color .3s
        }

        .case:hover .case__tag {
            color: var(--white)
        }

        .case__title {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 28px);
            letter-spacing: -.02em;
            line-height: 1.1
        }

        .case__kpi {
            margin-top: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--red);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 3px 10px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: background .3s
        }

        .case:hover .case__kpi {
            background: var(--black)
        }

        /* ---- Team ---- */
        .team {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--black);
            padding: 140px 36px
        }

        .team__grid {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 24px
        }

        .member {
            position: relative
        }

        .member__img {
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 4/5;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: grayscale(100%);
            transition: filter .4s
        }

        .member:hover .member__img {
            filter: grayscale(0%)
        }

        .member__info {
            padding: 20px 0 0
        }

        .member__name {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: 22px;
            letter-spacing: -.02em;
            line-height: 1
        }

        .member__role {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--red);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-top: 6px;
            font-weight: 700
        }

        .member__bio {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--muted-dark);
            margin-top: 10px;
            line-height: 1.5
        }

        .member__socials {
            margin-top: 14px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px
        }

        .member__socials a {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border: 1px solid var(--black);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 11px;
            transition: all .25s
        }

        .member__socials a:hover {
            background: var(--red);
            border-color: var(--red);
            color: var(--white)
        }

        /* ---- Testimonials carousel ---- */
        .testimonials {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 140px 36px
        }

        .testi-grid {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px
        }

        .testi {
            background: #0c0c0c;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            padding: 36px 30px;
            position: relative;
            transition: all .4s
        }

        .testi:hover {
            background: var(--red);
            border-color: var(--red);
            transform: translateY(-8px)
        }

        .testi__stars {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            color: var(--red);
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: color .3s
        }

        .testi:hover .testi__stars {
            color: var(--white)
        }

        .testi__quote {
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-size: 19px;
            line-height: 1.45;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-style: italic
        }

        .testi__who {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
            transition: border-color .3s
        }

        .testi:hover .testi__who {
            border-top-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .3)
        }

        .testi__avatar {
            width: 46px;
            height: 46px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: grayscale(100%);
            transition: filter .3s
        }

        .testi:hover .testi__avatar {
            filter: grayscale(0%)
        }

        .testi__name {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px
        }

        .testi__role {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--muted);
            transition: color .3s
        }

        .testi:hover .testi__role {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .8)
        }

        /* ---- Clients ---- */
        .clients {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 100px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line)
        }

        .clients__head {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            padding: 0 36px;
            text-align: center
        }

        .clients__head h2 {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 60px);
            line-height: .95;
            letter-spacing: -.03em;
            margin-top: 18px
        }

        .clients__marquee {
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 20px 0
        }

        .clients__track {
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(26px, 3.8vw, 50px);
            letter-spacing: -.02em;
            animation: scroll 50s linear infinite
        }

        .clients__track span:nth-child(even) {
            color: var(--red);
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-weight: 400;
            font-style: italic
        }

        /* ---- FAQ ---- */
        .faq {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--black);
            padding: 140px 36px
        }

        .faq__grid {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto
        }

        .faq-item {
            border-top: 1.5px solid var(--line-dark);
            padding: 28px 0;
            cursor: pointer
        }

        .faq-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--line-dark)
        }

        .faq-item__q {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px
        }

        .faq-item__q h4 {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 26px);
            letter-spacing: -.02em;
            line-height: 1.3
        }

        .faq-item__plus {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--black);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            transition: all .3s;
        }

        .faq-item__plus::before,
        .faq-item__plus::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 14px;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--black);
            transition: transform .3s, background .3s
        }

        .faq-item__plus {
            position: relative
        }

        .faq-item__plus::after {
            transform: rotate(90deg)
        }

        .faq-item.active .faq-item__plus {
            background: var(--red);
            border-color: var(--red)
        }

        .faq-item.active .faq-item__plus::before,
        .faq-item.active .faq-item__plus::after {
            background: var(--white)
        }

        .faq-item.active .faq-item__plus::after {
            transform: rotate(0deg)
        }

        .faq-item__a {
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: max-height .5s cubic-bezier(.2, .8, .2, 1)
        }

        .faq-item__a p {
            padding-top: 18px;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--muted-dark)
        }

        .faq-item.active .faq-item__a {
            max-height: 300px
        }

        /* ---- Blog / Insights ---- */
        .blog {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 140px 36px
        }

        .blog__grid {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 30px
        }

        .post {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all .4s;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column
        }

        .post:hover {
            border-color: var(--red);
            transform: translateY(-6px)
        }

        .post__img {
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 3/2;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: grayscale(100%);
            transition: filter .4s, transform .5s
        }

        .post:hover .post__img {
            filter: grayscale(0%);
            transform: scale(1.04)
        }

        .post__body {
            padding: 28px;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column
        }

        .post__meta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--muted);
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 600
        }

        .post__meta .dot {
            color: var(--red)
        }

        .post h3 {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: 22px;
            letter-spacing: -.02em;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 14px
        }

        .post p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
            flex: 1;
            margin-bottom: 18px
        }

        .post__read {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--red);
            text-transform: uppercase
        }

        /* ---- Contact ---- */
        .contact {
            background: var(--red);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 140px 36px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .contact::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -100px;
            left: -100px;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .2);
            border-radius: 50%
        }

        .contact::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -200px;
            right: -200px;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .15);
            border-radius: 50%
        }

        .contact__inner {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 80px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1
        }

        .contact .chapter {
            color: var(--white);
            border-color: var(--white)
        }

        .contact__left h2 {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(44px, 7.5vw, 120px);
            line-height: .92;
            letter-spacing: -.04em;
            margin: 24px 0 32px
        }

        .contact__left h2 em {
            font-family: var(--f-serif);
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 400
        }

        .contact__left h2 .outline {
            -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--white);
            color: transparent
        }

        .contact__left>p {
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 480px;
            margin-bottom: 44px;
            opacity: .95
        }

        .contact__cta-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 14px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 40px
        }

        .contact__list {
            list-style: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 2;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .3);
            padding-top: 28px
        }

        .contact__list li {
            display: flex;
            gap: 14px;
            align-items: baseline
        }

        .contact__list li span {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 34px;
            font-weight: 700;
            opacity: .7;
            flex-shrink: 0
        }

        /* Form */
        .form {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--black);
            padding: 44px 40px;
            position: relative;
            border: 2px solid var(--black);
            box-shadow: 14px 14px 0 var(--black)
        }

        .form__row {
            border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--black);
            padding: 14px 0
        }

        .form__row:last-of-type {
            margin-bottom: 24px
        }

        .form__row label span {
            display: block;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--red);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            text-transform: uppercase
        }

        .form__row input,
        .form__row textarea,
        .form__row select {
            width: 100%;
            border: none;
            background: transparent;
            font-family: var(--f-body);
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--black);
            outline: none;
            resize: none
        }

        .form__row input::placeholder,
        .form__row textarea::placeholder {
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, .35);
            font-style: italic;
            font-family: var(--f-serif)
        }

        .form__submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 13px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            transition: background .25s
        }

        .form__submit:hover {
            background: var(--red)
        }

        .form__msg {
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--red);
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(6px);
            transition: all .3s
        }

        .form__msg.show {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0)
        }

        /* ---- Footer ---- */
        .footer {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 80px 36px 0;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .footer__big {
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: clamp(80px, 22vw, 340px);
            line-height: .85;
            letter-spacing: -.05em;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--white) 30%, transparent);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            text-align: center
        }

        .footer__row {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 40px;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line)
        }

        .footer__col h5 {
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 2.5px;
            color: var(--red);
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700
        }

        .footer__col p,
        .footer__col a {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.9;
            color: var(--muted)
        }

        .footer__col a:hover {
            color: var(--white)
        }

        .footer__bottom {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 30px 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--muted);
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 14px
        }

        .footer__strip {
            margin-top: 0;
            padding: 20px 0;
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-family: var(--f-display);
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .3);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--line)
        }

        /* ---- Floating WhatsApp ---- */
        .float-wa {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 24px;
            right: 24px;
            z-index: 900;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: var(--red);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(227, 6, 19, .4);
            animation: floatBob 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
            transition: transform .25s;
        }

        .float-wa:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1)
        }

        .float-wa::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -6px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid var(--red);
            opacity: .6;
            animation: ripple 2s infinite
        }

        @keyframes ripple {
            0% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: .6
            }

            100% {
                transform: scale(1.6);
                opacity: 0
            }
        }

        @keyframes floatBob {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0)
            }

            50% {
                transform: translateY(-5px)
            }
        }

        /* =========================================================
   RESPONSIVE — mobile-first polish
   ========================================================= */
        @media(max-width:1200px) {
            .services__grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr)
            }

            .blog__grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr)
            }

            .team__grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr)
            }

            .testi-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr
            }

            .hero__side {
                display: none
            }
        }

        @media(max-width:1000px) {
            .nav__links {
                display: none
            }

            .nav__burger {
                display: flex
            }

            .nav__cta {
                display: none
            }

            .pkg-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr
            }

            .pkg--hero {
                transform: none
            }

            .pkg--hero:hover {
                transform: translate(-6px, -6px)
            }

            .stats__grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr)
            }

            .stat:nth-child(2) {
                border-right: none
            }

            .stat:nth-child(1),
            .stat:nth-child(2) {
                border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--line-dark)
            }

            .contact__inner,
            .about__inner {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 48px
            }

            .station {
                grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
                gap: 20px
            }

            .station__img {
                display: none
            }

            .work__grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr)
            }

            .case:nth-child(1) {
                grid-column: span 4;
                aspect-ratio: 2/1
            }

            .case:nth-child(n+2) {
                grid-column: span 2;
                aspect-ratio: 1
            }
        }

        @media(max-width:720px) {
            .nav {
                padding: 14px 20px
            }

            .announce {
                font-size: 10px;
                letter-spacing: 1px
            }

            .hero {
                padding: 70px 20px 50px;
                min-height: auto
            }

            .hero__meta {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 8px
            }

            .hero__title {
                font-size: clamp(44px, 13vw, 80px);
                margin: 24px 0
            }

            .line--3 {
                padding-left: 0
            }

            .line--4 {
                gap: 12px
            }

            .line--4 .arrow {
                display: none
            }

            .hero__foot {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 24px
            }

            .stats,
            .services,
            .process,
            .packages,
            .clients,
            .contact,
            .about,
            .team,
            .work,
            .faq,
            .blog,
            .testimonials,
            .cta-block {
                padding: 70px 20px
            }

            .stats__grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr
            }

            .stat {
                border-right: none !important;
                border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--line-dark)
            }

            .stat:last-child {
                border-bottom: none
            }

            .section-head {
                margin-bottom: 50px
            }

            .services__grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 1px
            }

            .service-card {
                min-height: auto;
                padding: 32px 24px
            }

            .service-card__img {
                height: 200px
            }

            .station {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 10px;
                padding: 28px 10px
            }

            .station:hover {
                padding-left: 16px;
                padding-right: 16px
            }

            .station__no {
                font-size: 40px
            }

            .blog__grid,
            .team__grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr
            }

            .work__grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 12px
            }

            .case:nth-child(n) {
                grid-column: span 1;
                aspect-ratio: 4/3
            }

            .footer__row {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: 30px
            }

            .footer__bottom {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center
            }

            .form {
                padding: 28px 22px;
                box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 var(--black)
            }

            .contact__left h2 {
                font-size: 48px
            }

            .marquee__track,
            .clients__track {
                font-size: 18px;
                gap: 24px
            }

            .cta-banner {
                padding: 40px 20px
            }

            .cta-banner__row {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 16px
            }

            .about__media-stamp {
                width: 110px;
                height: 110px;
                font-size: 11px;
                bottom: -20px;
                right: -10px
            }

            .float-wa {
                width: 54px;
                height: 54px;
                bottom: 18px;
                right: 18px
            }

            .hero__bg {
                display: none
            }

            .btn {
                padding: 14px 20px;
                font-size: 11px
            }
        }

        @media(max-width:400px) {
            .hero__title {
                font-size: 46px
            }

            .section-title {
                font-size: 38px
            }

            .pkg {
                padding: 30px 22px
            }

            .pkg__name {
                font-size: 34px
            }
        }

        /* Reduce motion */
        @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce) {

            *,
            *::before,
            *::after {
                animation-duration: .01ms !important;
                transition-duration: .01ms !important
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Grain + cursor -->
    <div class="grain" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="cursor" id="cursor" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="cursor-dot" id="cursorDot" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <!-- ─── ANNOUNCEMENT BAR ─── -->
    <div class="announce">
        🔥 Q2 slots closing soon — <a href="#contact">book a free growth audit →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- ─── NAVIGATION ─── -->
    <header class="nav" id="nav">
        <a href="#" class="nav__logo" aria-label="Adybros Marketing">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" width="34" height="34" aria-hidden="true">
                <polygon points="20,4 36,36 24,36 20,26 16,36 4,36" fill="var(--red)" />
                <polygon points="20,4 28,20 24,20 20,12" fill="var(--white)" />
            </svg>
            <span>ADYBROS<em>®</em></span>
        </a>
        <nav class="nav__links">
            <a href="#about">About</a>
            <a href="#services">Services</a>
            <a href="#process">Process</a>
            <a href="#work">Work</a>
            <a href="#packages">Packages</a>
            <a href="#team">Team</a>
            <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        </nav>
        <a href="#contact" class="nav__cta">
            <span>Get Started</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14">
                <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"
                    stroke-linecap="square" />
            </svg>
        </a>
        <button class="nav__burger" id="burger" aria-label="Toggle menu">
            <i></i><i></i><i></i>
        </button>
    </header>

    <!-- Mobile drawer -->
    <nav class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#process">Process</a>
        <a href="#work">Work</a>
        <a href="#packages">Packages</a>
        <a href="#team">Team</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="cta">Get Started →</a>
    </nav>

    <!-- ─── HERO ─── -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero__bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <div class="hero__meta">
            <span class="hero__meta-id">[ A-001 / 2026 ]</span>
            <span class="hero__meta-loc">BAREILLY · DELHI · GLOBAL</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="hero__title">
            <span class="line line--1">Turning</span>
            <span class="line line--2">businesses</span>
            <span class="line line--3">into <em>leads</em> &amp;</span>
            <span class="line line--4">
                <span class="slash">SALES</span>
                <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 120 60" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path d="M5 30 L110 30 M85 8 L110 30 L85 52" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="6" fill="none"
                        stroke-linecap="square" />
                </svg>
                <span class="machines">machines.</span>
            </span>
        </h1>

        <div class="hero__foot">
            <div class="hero__blurb">
                <span class="dot"></span>
                <p>A performance marketing studio engineered for growth-hungry brands. We don't just post — we <em>print
                        pipeline</em>.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hero__cta-row">
                <a href="#contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book Free Audit</a>
                <a href="#packages" class="btn btn--ghost">See Packages</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="hero__side">
            <div class="stamp">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 160 160" width="130" height="130">
                    <defs>
                        <path id="circ" d="M 80,80 m -60,0 a 60,60 0 1,1 120,0 a 60,60 0 1,1 -120,0" />
                    </defs>
                    <text font-family="Space Grotesk" font-size="11" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="2"
                        fill="currentColor">
                        <textPath href="#circ">TRUSTED BY GROWING BRANDS · EST. 2022 · ROI OBSESSED · </textPath>
                    </text>
                    <polygon points="80,55 95,105 55,75 105,75 65,105" fill="var(--red)" />
                </svg>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </section>

    <!-- ─── MARQUEE ─── -->
    <div class="marquee" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="marquee__track">
            <span>META ADS</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>SEO</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>YOUTUBE</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>WHATSAPP CRM</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>LEAD ENGINE</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>CREATIVE STUDIO</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>FUNNELS</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>LINKEDIN</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>INFLUENCER</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>PR HUB</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>META ADS</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>SEO</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>YOUTUBE</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>WHATSAPP CRM</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>LEAD ENGINE</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>CREATIVE STUDIO</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>FUNNELS</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>LINKEDIN</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>INFLUENCER</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
            <span>PR HUB</span><span class="bullet">●</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ─── STATS ─── -->
    <section class="stats">
        <div class="section-head">
            <span class="eyebrow">Receipts, not promises</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">The scoreboard <em>speaks</em> louder than the pitch.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="stats__grid">
            <article class="stat">
                <div class="stat__num" data-target="400" data-suffix="+">0</div>
                <div class="stat__label">Ads Delivered</div>
                <div class="stat__bar"><i data-width="82%"></i></div>
            </article>
            <article class="stat">
                <div class="stat__num"><span class="prefix">₹</span><span data-target="12" data-suffix="L+">0</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat__label">Spent on Campaigns</div>
                <div class="stat__bar"><i data-width="68%"></i></div>
            </article>
            <article class="stat">
                <div class="stat__num"><span class="prefix">₹</span><span data-target="3" data-suffix="Cr+">0</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat__label">Sales Generated</div>
                <div class="stat__bar"><i data-width="94%"></i></div>
            </article>
            <article class="stat">
                <div class="stat__num" data-target="38" data-suffix="+">0</div>
                <div class="stat__label">Brands Scaled</div>
                <div class="stat__bar"><i data-width="76%"></i></div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ─── ABOUT ─── -->
    <section class="about" id="about">
        <div class="about__inner">
            <div class="about__media">
                <img class="about__media-main"
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=900&q=80"
                    alt="Adybros team at work" loading="lazy">
                <span class="about__tag">// THE STUDIO</span>
                <div class="about__media-stamp" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="about__body">
                <span class="chapter">CH. 01 — WHO WE ARE</span>
                <h2 style="margin-top:24px">We're the growth partner your <em>competitors</em> wish they had.</h2>
                <p>Adybros Marketing was built on a simple obsession — <em>pipeline over posts.</em> We stopped caring
                    about vanity metrics years ago. Instead, we wake up asking one question: how much revenue did we
                    move this week?</p>
                <p>Founded by <strong>Aakarshit Pathak</strong> and <strong>Lakshya Bhatnagar</strong>, we've grown into
                    a tight team of strategists, media buyers, creatives, and CRM engineers who treat your ad spend like
                    it's our own money.</p>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn btn--primary">Let's Talk Growth →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ─── CTA BANNER 1 ─── -->
    <section class="cta-banner">
        <div class="cta-banner__strip" aria-hidden="true">
            <span>YOUR AD SPEND.</span><span>our obsession.</span>
            <span>YOUR GROWTH.</span><span>our scoreboard.</span>
            <span>YOUR BRAND.</span><span>our battleground.</span>
            <span>YOUR AD SPEND.</span><span>our obsession.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-banner__row">
            <p>Talking is free. So is the first audit.</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn--dark">Book Audit →</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ─── SERVICES (9 service cards with real images) ─── -->
    <section class="services" id="services">
        <div class="section-head center">
            <span class="chapter">CH. 02 — WHAT WE DO</span>
            <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:24px">Full-stack <em>digital marketing</em>.<br>Under one roof.
            </h2>
            <p class="section-lead" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto">Nine disciplines. One integrated growth
                engine. Every service is optional — but none of them feel optional once you see the numbers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="services__grid">
            <article class="service-card">
                <img class="service-card__img"
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?w=700&q=80"
                    alt="Performance advertising" loading="lazy">
                <span class="service-card__no">01 / PAID MEDIA</span>
                <h3>Performance Advertising</h3>
                <p>Meta, Google, YouTube &amp; LinkedIn campaigns engineered for ROAS. Lead gen, awareness, retargeting
                    — we run it all.</p>
                <a href="#contact" class="service-card__arrow">Explore <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14">
                        <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" />
                    </svg></a>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <img class="service-card__img"
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1432888498266-38ffec3eaf0a?w=700&q=80" alt="SEO"
                    loading="lazy">
                <span class="service-card__no">02 / ORGANIC</span>
                <h3>SEO &amp; Content</h3>
                <p>Rank for the searches your buyers actually make. On-page audits, link building, and content that
                    earns clicks.</p>
                <a href="#contact" class="service-card__arrow">Explore <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14">
                        <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" />
                    </svg></a>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <img class="service-card__img"
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611162617474-5b21e879e113?w=700&q=80" alt="Social Media"
                    loading="lazy">
                <span class="service-card__no">03 / SOCIAL</span>
                <h3>Social Media Management</h3>
                <p>Instagram, Facebook, LinkedIn, YouTube. Dedicated managers, content calendars, and engagement that
                    compounds.</p>
                <a href="#contact" class="service-card__arrow">Explore <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14">
                        <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" />
                    </svg></a>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <img class="service-card__img"
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492691527719-9d1e07e534b4?w=700&q=80" alt="Video production"
                    loading="lazy">
                <span class="service-card__no">04 / MEDIA LAB</span>
                <h3>Video &amp; Content Production</h3>
                <p>On-site shoots, studio setups, drone cinematics. 45–90s reels, product videos, and scroll-stopping
                    creatives.</p>
                <a href="#contact" class="service-card__arrow">Explore <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14">
                        <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" />
                    </svg></a>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <img class="service-card__img"
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559028012-481c04fa702d?w=700&q=80" alt="Branding design"
                    loading="lazy">
                <span class="service-card__no">05 / DESIGN</span>
                <h3>Branding &amp; Creative Design</h3>
                <p>Logos, brand systems, carousels, static ads, landing pages. Visual identity that stops the scroll and
                    earns trust.</p>
                <a href="#contact" class="service-card__arrow">Explore <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14">
                        <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" />
                    </svg></a>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <img class="service-card__img"
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7?w=700&q=80" alt="Lead generation"
                    loading="lazy">
                <span class="service-card__no">06 / LEAD ENGINE</span>
                <h3>Lead Generation &amp; Funnels</h3>
                <p>Landing pages, lead magnets, CRM integration. We build the full funnel: Ad → Page → CRM → Follow-up.
                </p>
                <a href="#contact" class="service-card__arrow">Explore <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14">
                        <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" />
                    </svg></a>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <img class="service-card__img"
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556157382-97eda2d62296?w=700&q=80" alt="WhatsApp marketing"
                    loading="lazy">
                <span class="service-card__no">07 / CRM</span>
