    <!-- ─── FAQ ─── -->
    <section class="faq" id="faq">
        <div class="section-head center">
            <span class="chapter">CH. 05 — ANSWERS</span>
            <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:24px">Questions, <em>handled</em>.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="faq__grid">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-item__q">
                    <h4>How quickly can we see results?</h4>
                    <div class="faq-item__plus"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item__a">
                    <p>Most performance clients see measurable improvement within 14–21 days (reduced CPL, improved
                        CTR). Meaningful revenue lift typically lands in weeks 6–10 once creative, audiences and landing
                        pages have been optimized.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-item__q">
                    <h4>Do I need a minimum ad budget?</h4>
                    <div class="faq-item__plus"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item__a">
                    <p>We recommend a minimum ad spend of ₹50,000/month on top of the retainer for our Impact package —
                        it's the floor where Meta's learning algorithm can actually optimize. For Influence and
                        Authority, ₹1.5L+ is ideal.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-item__q">
                    <h4>What industries do you specialize in?</h4>
                    <div class="faq-item__plus"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item__a">
                    <p>Real estate, D2C, luxury, hospitality, education, and B2B services. But our system is
                        industry-agnostic — if your customer is online, we can find them.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-item__q">
                    <h4>Will I get a dedicated point of contact?</h4>
                    <div class="faq-item__plus"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item__a">
                    <p>Yes. Every account gets a dedicated manager plus direct Slack/WhatsApp access to the founders.
                        You'll never feel like a ticket number.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-item__q">
                    <h4>Is there a long-term contract?</h4>
